{"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/objc(cs)NSObject"],"title":"Inherits From","kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom"},{"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/SQ","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/SH","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/s8SendableP"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","externalID":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"class","modules":[{"name":"OUDSTokensSemantic"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Kind of semantic tokens which will wrap a combination of "},{"code":"FontCompositeRawToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" depending to size classes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Kind of composite token with multiple values, but not named “composite” because this word is already used in the design system.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Allows to gather the multiple-value tokens from ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Figma"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" inside one object.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If a font token exists with its value depending to the size class, it must be packed in such ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontcompositerawtokens"]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/init(_:)","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/init(compact:regular:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/compact","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/regular"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties"},{"anchor":"Instance-Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/fontToken(for:)","doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens\/isEqual(_:)"],"title":"Instance Methods"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["        \/\/ Assuming in Figma with have a font semantic token typeDisplayLarge,","        \/\/ with values depending to size class. These values are defined as font composite raw tokens.","        let typeBold850 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize850, lineHeight: fontLineHeight1050, weight: fontWeight700, letterSpacing: fontLetterSpacing850)","        let typeBold1450 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize1450, lineHeight: fontLineHeight1850, weight: fontWeight700, letterSpacing: fontLetterSpacing1450)","","        \/\/ Then the develoment team declares an \"higher\" level font semantic token","        \/\/ inside FontCompositeSemanticTokens protocol,","        \/\/ and defined inside OUDSTheme+FontCompositeSemanticTokens extension","        var typeDisplayLarge: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens {","            MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(compact: FontRawTokens.typeBold850, regular: FontRawTokens.typeBold1450)","        }","","        \/\/ If the same font is used whatever the size class is","        var typeDisplayLarge: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens { MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(FontRawTokens.typeBold650) }","","        \/\/ The theme exposes both generated elevation semantic tokens and \"crafted\" higher level elevation semantic tokens.","        \/\/ It is recommended to use the higher level version as it is less error-prone."],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The case of this ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" is quite particular because in fact it contains ","type":"text"},{"code":"FontCompositeRawToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(i.e. raw tokens) instead of semantic tokens.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In fact there is not “font composite semantic tokens” defined in the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Figma"}]},{"text":" kit.","type":"text"}]},{"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.8.0"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSTokensSemantic\/documentation\/OUDSTokensSemantic\/MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","interfaceLanguage":"swi